# ── Heterogeneous dual manufacture (condition 6) ─────────────────────────────
# The independently-built ggen 26.7.13 (installed at ~/.cargo/bin/ggen, a
# DIFFERENT toolchain/build than the debug binary above -- built from an
# earlier commit predating this repo's ggen.toml schema evolution) was run
